'''利德尼'''（Lydney）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]]的一個小鎮和[[民政教區|民政教區]]。利德尼位於塞文河西岸，靠近迪恩森林。據2001年人口普查，利德尼有人口8,960人<ref>=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadTableView.do?a=7&b=549268&c=Lydney&d=14&e=16&g=448000&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&o=362&m=0&r=1&s=1373194900364&enc=1&dsFamilyId=75 {{Wayback|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadTableView.do?a=7&b=549268&c=Lydney&d=14&e=16&g=448000&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&o=362&m=0&r=1&s=1373194900364&enc=1&dsFamilyId=75 |date=20161011034519 }}</ref>。2011年人口普查時減少至8,766人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11126192&c=Lydney&d=16&e=62&g=6427159&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1427472876600&enc=1|title=Town population 2011. Retrieved 27 March 2015|accessdate=2016-03-11|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402113145/https://neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11126192&c=Lydney&d=16&e=62&g=6427159&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1427472876600&enc=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
